<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_xh5_y4d_br">
 <title>Hive Properties and Configuration Files</title>
    <conbody>
        <p><indexterm>Hive Streaming destination<indexterm>using configuration files or adding
                    properties</indexterm></indexterm>You can configure Hive Streaming to use Hive
            and Hadoop configuration files and additional properties:<dl>
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>Configuration files</dt>
                    <dd>The following configuration files are required for the Hive Streaming
                            destination:<ul
                            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/HiveStreamingFiles"
                            id="ul_stc_qjf_lt">
                            <li/>
                        </ul></dd>
                    <dd>To use the configuration files:<ol
                            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/OL-HiveConfigSteps"
                            id="ol_ilw_sbs_dw">
                            <li/>
                        </ol></dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>Individual properties</dt>
                    <dd>You can configure individual Hive properties in the destination. To add a
                        Hive property, specify the exact property name and the value. The
                        destination does not validate the property names or values.<note>Individual
                            properties override properties defined in the configuration files.
                            </note><draft-comment author="Loretta">Versions of this used in Hive
                            Metadata processor and Hive Metastore destination. Make sure changes
                            from here go there, as needed. 6/2016.</draft-comment></dd>
                </dlentry>
            </dl></p>
    </conbody>
</concept>
